Install PyTest:
pip install -U pytest
and
pip3 install -U pytest

pip install html-testRunner

do "import HtmlTestRunner" to your test file
or
do "import HTMLTestRunner" to your test file

add folder "HtmlReports" to your project

add path to your test file footer:
 if __name__ == '__main__':
    unittest.main(testRunner=HtmlTestRunner.HTMLTestRunner(output='./HtmlReports'))

run your test file from Terminal like:
python unittest14.py
or
py unittest14.py